6378137.0  'wkt_bbox_hearthSize' STORE

PI $wkt_bbox_la * 180 / COS

'(('

',' 5 JOIN
'))'
'' 3 JOIN
'POLYGON' SWAP ' ' 2 JOIN
%>

%warpscript
//import macroWKT token latitudePool longitudePool nbKMPool

//
// Load last point before 01/01/2016
//

[ $token 'data.fuel.france' { 'type' 'gazole' } 1451606401000000 -1  ] FETCH

[    
    SWAP
    $latitudePool $longitudePool $nbKMPool 1000 *
    $macroWKT EVAL EVAL
    0.2 false GEO.WKT mapper.geo.within
    0
    0
    0
] MAP 
NONEMPTY
'list' STORE

[] 'stations' STORE
$list
<%
    LABELS 'id' GET
    $stations SWAP + 'stations' STORE
%>
FOREACH
{
    'resultList'
    $list
    'nbStations'
    $list SIZE
    'stationsId'
    $stations LSORT
}

z.angularBind("nbStations", z.get("nbStations")) var stations = z.get("stationsId").toString stations = stations.replace("[", "").replace("]", "") z.angularBind("allStations",stations) println("%angular

") println("%angular

There is {{nbStations}} stations around. Those stations are {{ allStations }}.

")

%warpscript
//import macroWKT token latitudePool longitudePool nbKMPool

$token AUTHENTICATE

1000000 MAXBUCKETS
20000000 LIMIT

[ $token 'data.fuel.france' { 'type' 'gazole' } 1451606401000000 NOW  ] FETCH

'allGTS' STORE

[ $allGTS bucketizer.mean 0 1 d 0 ] BUCKETIZE
FILLPREVIOUS

[ SWAP [ 'type' ] reducer.mean.exclude-nulls ] REDUCE

[ SWAP bucketizer.mean 0 30 d 0 ] BUCKETIZE

0 GET 'mean-values-all-stations-France' RENAME
'meanGTS' STORE

[ $allGTS [] { 'id' '~29.*' } filter.bylabels ] FILTER

[ SWAP bucketizer.mean 0 1 d 0 ] BUCKETIZE
FILLPREVIOUS

[ SWAP bucketizer.mean 0 30 d 0 ] BUCKETIZE

[ SWAP [ 'type' ] reducer.mean.exclude-nulls ] REDUCE

0 GET 'mean-values-all-stations-Finistère' RENAME
'finisterGTS' STORE

[    
    $allGTS
    $latitudePool $longitudePool $nbKMPool 1000 *
    $macroWKT EVAL EVAL
    0.2 false GEO.WKT mapper.geo.within
    0
    0
    0
] MAP 
NONEMPTY

[ SWAP bucketizer.mean 0 1 d 0 ] BUCKETIZE
FILLPREVIOUS

[ SWAP bucketizer.mean 0 30 d 0 ] BUCKETIZE

[ SWAP [ 'type' ] reducer.mean.exclude-nulls ] REDUCE

0 GET 'mean-values-all-stations-Near-By' RENAME
'nearBy' STORE

{
    'result3GTS'
    [ $meanGTS $finisterGTS $nearBy ]
}
